Hello Raffaella,
As requested, Tower Insurance will share all information, laboratory test r=
esults, supporting information, raw data & photographs from the testing pro=
cess as soon as we receive them =E2=80=93 this will be in individual files,=
 and not within the context of a full report with further relevant context =
and commentary.
All the above items will be incorporated into a full covering report which =
will take a little while longer to produce. The full report will also be pr=
ovided to you as soon as we have received it.

Thank you so much for your time and input you shared onsite with us, while =
we conducted the tests. I look forward to sharing the results with you as s=
oon as possible.
Best Regards,
Grant.

[cid:image001.png@01DC482F.A2AD2030]
