<div class=3D"WordSection1">
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Hello Raffaella,<o:=
p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">As requested, Tower=
 Insurance will share all information, laboratory test results, supporting =
information, raw data &amp; photographs from the testing process as soon as=
 we receive them =E2=80=93 this will be in individual
 files, and not within the context of a full report with further relevant c=
ontext and commentary.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">All the above items=
 will be incorporated into a full covering report which will take a little =
while longer to produce. The full report will also be provided to you as so=
on as we have received it.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></=
span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Thank you so much f=
or your time and input you shared onsite with us, while we conducted the te=
sts. I look forward to sharing the results with you as soon as possible.<o:=
p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Best Regards,<o:p><=
/o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Grant. <o:p></o:p><=
/span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></=
span></p>
